  <h2>Principles</h2>

  <p>The WHATWG is guided by <a href="/principles">Principles</a> of openness, utility, efficiency and freedom.

  <h2>Policies</h2>

  <p>The WHATWG participants operate under a number of policies:

  <ol>
   <li><a href="/ipr-policy">Intellectual Property Rights Policy</a>

   <li><a href="/workstream-policy">Workstream Policy</a>

   <li><a href="/code-of-conduct">Code of Conduct</a>

   <li><a href="/working-mode">Working Mode</a>
  </ol>

  <p>Additionally, the WHATWG Steering Group was created by the <a href="/sg-agreement">Steering Group Agreement</a> and operates under the <a href="/sg-policy">Steering Group Policy</a>.

